com.radiantlogic.iddm.base

Interface DeleteOperations<IN extends DeleteRequest,OUT extends DeleteResponse>

  • Type Parameters:
    IN - The request type accepted by this class
    OUT - The response type returned by this class
    All Superinterfaces:
    Connector

    public interface DeleteOperations<IN extends DeleteRequest,OUT extends DeleteResponse>
extends Connector
    Defines methods for connectors that can perform delete operations against the backend data source.

    To use, the developer needs only to create a class that implements this interface and each of its methods (as no default implementations are provided). For example: 

    
 class CustomConnector implements DeleteOperations<LdapDeleteRequest, LdapResponse<String>>
